lead_paragraph: Potential Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton pointed out her differences with President Barack Obama on Tuesday over his decision not to arm moderate Syrian rebels, as neighboring Iraq struggles to cope with extremist spillover from Syria.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Notes Distance From Obama on Syria Rebels
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Notes Distance From Obama on Syria Rebels
